name: they collected cutlery
description: After the town of Talent, Oregon, was decimated in an act of arson, the community went through the rubble and compiled what was left of the homes. They found melted statues. They found ashes. They collected cutlery. Shot on vintage Canon AE-1 camera with Portra 400 film, scan created directly from the negative. 3130 x 2075 px
